          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-096-ROGP-line-1" n="1">The Queen has lately lost a part</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-096-ROGP-line-2" n="2">Of her entirely English heart,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-096-ROGP-line-3" n="3">For want of which by way of botch,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-096-ROGP-line-4" n="4">She pieced it up again with Scotch.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-096-ROGP-line-5" n="5">Blessed revolution, which creates</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-096-ROGP-line-6" n="6">Divided hearts, united states.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-096-ROGP-line-7" n="7">See how the double nation lies;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-096-ROGP-line-8" n="8">Like a rich coat with skirts of frieze:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-096-ROGP-line-9" n="9">As if a man in making posies</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-096-ROGP-line-10" n="10">Should bundle thistles up with roses.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-096-ROGP-line-11" n="11">Whoever yet a union saw</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-096-ROGP-line-12" n="12">Of kingdoms, without faith or law.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-096-ROGP-line-13" n="13">Henceforward let no statesman dare,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-096-ROGP-line-14" n="14">A kingdom to a ship compare;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-096-ROGP-line-15" n="15">Lest he should call our commonweal,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-096-ROGP-line-16" n="16">A vessel with a double keel:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-096-ROGP-line-17" n="17">Which just like ours, new rigged and manned,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-096-ROGP-line-18" n="18">And got about a league from land,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-096-ROGP-line-19" n="19">By change of wind to leeward side</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-096-ROGP-line-20" n="20">The pilot knew not how to guide.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-096-ROGP-line-21" n="21">So tossing faction will o'erwhelm</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-096-ROGP-line-22" n="22">Our crazy double-bottomed realm.</l>
          </lg>
